ReferenceDocuments.name: HTAN-Instruction
ReferenceDocuments.description: Derivative entities include anything derived from a research participant.  Each derivative entity in your atlas must have a unique HTAN Identifier formatted as ::= _integer.  For example, if research participant 1 within the CHOP project has provided three samples, you would have three HTAN IDs, such as:  HTA4_1_1 HTA4_1_3 HTA4_1_8  If a single data file was generated from one of those samples, that file could have an HTAN ID such as  HTA4_1_42
